    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "Z and X live below A and S, in the bottom-left corner. Z is your pinky curling down, X is your ring finger. Weak fingers, so go easy and keep them honest. Curl down, tap, back to home."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "🔓",
      "title": "Weak fingers, light touch",
      "text": "Pinky and ring are the least obedient fingers you have. Don't slam, don't rush. A calm, even tap beats a fast miss every time."
    },
